        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Long-Term Care Tax Reduction Act of 2007 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to exclude from gross income distributions from an individual retirement account and other tax-exempt retirement plans used to pay long-term care insurance premiums.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
